name: Miguel Angel
text: This little Caesars is inside the Kmart and while I was at Kmart this last time I stopped by to get some garlic bread, They were fast and I took them to go since there is not much sitting space and it wasn't clean at the time. It is convenient and I would stop by again to pick up.
